#############################################################################################

This sketch prints latitude, longitude, pressure, altitude on both serial monitor and TFT

Components: GPS Module GT-U7, TFT 1.8" SPI, BMP180 (AZ-Delivery GY-68), 
            Push Button, 5 MOhm Resistor

GT-U7:
TXD --> RX2 (GPIO16)
RXD --> TX2 (GPIO17)
GND --> GND
VCC --> 3.3V 

TFT:
LED      --> 3.3V
SCK      --> D18 (VSPI-SCK)
SDA      --> D23 (VSPI-MOSI)
A0 (DC)  --> D32
RST      --> D4
CS       --> D5 (VSPI-SS)
GND      --> GND
VCC      --> 3.3V

BMP180:
VIN --> 3.3V
GND --> GND
SCL --> D22 (I2C-SCL)
SDA --> D21 (I2C-SDA)

SD: 
3v3  --> 3.3v 
GND  --> GND
SCK  --> D18 (VSPI-SCK)
MISO --> D19 (VSPI-MISC)
MOSI --> D23 (VSPI-MOSI)
CS   --> D15

Distance Reset (Prototype):
Button --> D33 + Resistor 5MOhm connected to GND (see picture)

